# Cursor Rules for Recipe Book Project

## Package Manager
- Always use `bun` instead of `npm` or `yarn` for package management
- Use `bun install` instead of `npm install`
- Use `bun add <package>` instead of `npm install <package>`
- Use `bun add -d <package>` instead of `npm install --save-dev <package>`
- Use `bun run <script>` instead of `npm run <script>`
- Use `bunx` instead of `npx` for running packages

## Project Context
- This is a React + TypeScript + Vite project
- Uses Vitest for testing
- Uses Tailwind CSS and shadcn/ui for UI
- Uses @atproto/api for Bluesky/ATProto integration
- Uses IndexedDB for local caching
